dc_title_s: Top Natural Gas Fields, United States, Summer 2014
dc_description_s: This polygon shapefile contains locations of natual gas fields in the United States. including existing Meter Points (receipt and delivery points). This layer is from the summer quarter update of 2014,This dataset may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data.
